&lt;li&gt;Build a standardized, repeatable migration framework that reduces per-customer effort over successive cohorts and scales with Cayuse’s growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and maintain the migration runbook, including tooling requirements, data validation standards, cutover procedures, rollback protocols, and customer communication templates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track program health through clear metrics and surface tradeoffs to senior leadership before they become critical.&lt;/li&gt;
